/*
 * RSOC Answer Engine — localized, region-aware backend.
 * Content (hooks + openers) is generated by the multilingual model per
 * (region, vertical, locale) and cached in Upstash so it's instant after the
 * first view. DEMO ONLY: advertisers/content are AI-generated and synthetic,
 * not legally-vetted ad inventory.
 */

